  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张图，说明FSKitBridge在macOS上的整体架构。核心问题是：用户怎么把自定义文件系统挂到系统里，同时保持沙盒安全。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FSKitBridge",
        "macOS",
        "sandbox"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以这张图要覆盖从系统发现、到扩展选举、再到实际运行时通信的完整链路？还是只聚焦运行时？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "discovery",
        "election",
        "runtime"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完整链路都要。特别是PKD（PlugInKit）的角色，很多人误以为FSKit扩展是App直接加载的，其实是系统托管的独立进程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PKD",
        "PlugInKit",
        "appex",
        "separate process at runtime"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我建议分三大块：左边是macOS系统层，中间是HostBundle也就是你的App包，右边是用户自己的后端进程。这样横向流动比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "macOS",
        "HostBundle",
        "Backend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。但HostBundle里面要再拆一层——FSKitExt.appex是嵌在App里的扩展包，实际跑在沙盒里，和Host进程是分开的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HostBundle",
        "FSKitExt.appex",
        "sandbox",
        "Host"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在HostBundle里画一个子图叫FSKitExt.appex，里面放FSOps节点，表示实际处理文件操作的地方。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FSKitExt.appex",
        "FSOps",
        "HostBundle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FSOps的具体实现是FSUnaryFileSystem加上各种Operations，这个要标出来。另外Host本身只做UI和enablement，不干实事。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FSUnaryFileSystem",
        "Operations",
        "Host",
        "UI",
        "enablement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "系统层这边，PKD负责discovery和election我理解，VFS节点是指内核里的FSKit host吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PKD",
        "discovery",
        "election",
        "VFS",
        "FSKit host"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，VFS是系统侧的文件系统宿主，它通过XPC和appex里的FSOps通信。这是苹果设计的标准路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VFS",
        "XPC",
        "FSOps",
        "appex"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了。我在macOS子图里加上PKD和VFS两个节点，PKD标注discovery/election/lifecycle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "macOS",
        "PKD",
        "VFS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "右边还需要一个独立的后端区域。用户的实际文件系统逻辑是用Rust或Python写的，跑在Custom.app里，通过TCP暴露服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
